CatDescriptText: "Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 27, 1958, page 23, reads: "Dandy Duffers Winners - Eight members of the Dandy Duffers Golf Club had something to smile about last Sunday at the Flamingo Hotel, as they received trophies at the organization's annual Awards Night ceremonies. Receiving trophies are, left to right, front row: Harry T. Irvin, Harding A. Smith, Henry Morgan and Everett Utterback. Back row: Jackson Wright, Orville Smith, Jack Kelly and Roscoe Young. Taking part in presentation of the trophies was Mrs. Daryl C. Chapman, far right. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Dandy Duffers, front row from left: Harry T. Irvin, Harding A. Smith, Henry Morgan, and Everett Utterback Sr.; back row: Jackson Wright, Orville Smith, Jack Kelly, Roscoe Young, and presenter of the trophies, Mrs. Daryl C. Chapman, posed at the Flamingo Hotel
